{"type":"message","id":"8182604e","parentId":"298dc54f","timestamp":"2026-04-22T09:50:40.998Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-22 17:50:40 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7) [msg:om_x100b51bdd03ec8b8c4d124cf38199c7]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51bdd03ec8b8c4d124cf38199c7\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"sender\": \"haidong\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 17:50 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"haidong (ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f70eb83737eac4282ce8bee3202593c7\",\n  \"name\": \"haidong\"\n}\n```\n\n选项b"}],"timestamp":1776851440996}}
{"type":"message","id":"15911193","parentId":"8182604e","timestamp":"2026-04-22T09:51:14.121Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户选择了选项B：继续 Phase 3 - fail2ban集成、标准化输出格式、外部安全工具集成。\n\nPhase 3内容：\n- fail2ban集成（优先级最高）\n- 标准化输出格式\n- lynis可选集成\n\n我需要继续实施Phase 3，添加这些功能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！开始 Phase 3：外部安全工具集成 🚀\n\n让我添加 fail2ban 集成、标准化输出格式和其他安全工具集成。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5x0nt85aq7i8_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n#\n# fail2ban Security Tools Integration for OpenClaw\n# Version: 1.0.0\n# Phase: 3 - External Security Tools Integration\n#\n# This script integrates fail2ban with OpenClaw healthcheck\n#\n\nset -e\n\n# Configuration\nLOG_FILE=\"/tmp/openclaw-fail2ban-integration.log\"\nCONFIG_DIR=\"/etc/fail2ban\"\n\n# Colors\nRED='\\033[0;31m'\nGREEN='\\033[0;32m'\nYELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nNC='\\033[0m'\n\nlog() {\n    echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] $1\" | tee -a \"$LOG_FILE\"\n}\n\nsuccess() {\n    echo -e \"${GREEN}[SUCCESS] $1${NC}\" | tee -a \"$LOG_FILE\"\n}\n\nwarn() {\n    echo -e \"${YELLOW}[WARNING] $1${NC}\" | tee -a \"$LOG_FILE\"\n}\n\nerror() {\n    echo -e \"${RED}[ERROR] $1${NC}\" | tee -a \"$LOG_FILE\"\n}\n\n# Check if running as root\nif [ \"$EUID\" -ne 0 ]; then\n    error \"This script must be run as root or with sudo\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\nlog \"Starting fail2ban integration for OpenClaw\"\n\n# Check if fail2ban is installed\nif ! command -v fail2ban-server &> /dev/null; then\n    warn \"fail2ban is not installed\"\n    read -p \"Do you want to install fail2ban? (y/n): \" -n 1 -r\n    echo\n    if [[ $REPLY =~ ^[Yy]$ ]]; then\n        log \"Installing fail2ban...\"\n        apt-get update && apt-get install -y fail2ban\n        success \"fail2ban installed\"\n    else\n        warn \"Skipping fail2ban installation\"\n        exit 0\n    fi\nfi\n\n# Check if fail2ban is running\nif ! systemctl is-active --quiet fail2ban; then\n    warn \"fail2ban is not running\"\n    read -p \"Do you want to start fail2ban? (y/n): \" -n 1 -r\n    echo\n    if [[ $REPLY =~ ^[Yy]$ ]]; then\n        systemctl enable fail2ban\n        systemctl start fail2ban\n        success \"fail2ban started\"\n    fi\nfi\n\n# Create OpenClaw-specific jail configuration\nlog \"Creating OpenClaw-specific fail2ban configuration...\"\n\ncat > /etc/fail2ban/jail.d/openclaw.conf << 'EOF'\n[openclaw-ssh]\nenabled = true\nport = ssh\nfilter = openclaw-ssh\nlogpath = /var/log/auth.log\nmaxretry = 5\nbantime = 3600\nfindtime = 600\naction = iptables-allports[name=openclaw]\n\n[openclaw-gateway]\nenabled = true\nport = 8080,8443,3000\nfilter = openclaw-gateway\nlogpath = /var/log/openclaw/gateway/*.log\nmaxretry = 10\nbantime = 1800\nfindtime = 300\naction = iptables-allports[name=openclaw-gateway]\n\n[openclaw-api]\nenabled = true\nport = 8080\nfilter = openclaw-api\nlogpath = /var/log/openclaw/api/*.log\nmaxretry = 20\nbantime = 600\nfindtime = 60\naction = iptables-allports[name=openclaw-api]\nEOF\n\n# Create OpenClaw filter definitions\nmkdir -p /etc/fail2ban/filter.d\n\n# SSH filter for OpenClaw\ncat > /etc/fail2ban/filter.d/openclaw-ssh.conf << 'EOF'\n[Definition]\nfailregex = ^%(__prefix_line)sFailed password for .* from <HOST>.*\n            ^%(__prefix_line)sROOT LOG REFUSED.* from <HOST>.*\n            ^%(__prefix_line)sMaximum authentication attempts exceeded for.* from <HOST>.*\nignoreregex =\nEOF\n\n# Gateway filter\ncat > /etc/fail2ban/filter.d/openclaw-gateway.conf << 'EOF'\n[Definition]\nfailregex = ^.*\\[error\\] .* client <HOST>.* unauthorized access$\n            ^.*\\[warn\\] .* repeated login attempts from <HOST>$\n            ^.*\\[security\\] .* brute force attempt from <HOST>$\nignoreregex =\nEOF\n\n# API filter\ncat > /etc/fail2ban/filter.d/openclaw-api.conf << 'EOF'\n[Definition]\nfailregex = ^.*401 Unauthorized.*from <HOST>$\n            ^.*403 Forbidden.*from <HOST>$\n            ^.*rate limit exceeded.*from <HOST>$\nignoreregex =\nEOF\n\n# Reload fail2ban\nsystemctl reload fail2ban\n\n# Display status\nsuccess \"fail2ban integration completed!\"\nlog \"Configuration files created:\"\nlog \"  - /etc/fail2ban/jail.d/openclaw.conf\"\nlog \"  - /etc/fail2ban/filter.d/openclaw-ssh.conf\"\nlog \"  - /etc/fail2ban/filter.d/openclaw-gateway.conf\"\nlog \"  - /etc/fail2ban/filter.d/openclaw-api.conf\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"📊 Current fail2ban status:\"\nfail2ban-client status\necho \"\"\necho \"🔍 To check specific jail:\"\necho \"   sudo fail2ban-client status openclaw-ssh\"\necho \"   sudo fail2ban-client status openclaw-gateway\"\necho \"\"\necho \"📝 To view banned IPs:\"\necho \"   sudo fail2ban-client banned openclaw-ssh\"\necho \"\"\necho \"🔓 To unban an IP:\"\necho \"   sudo fail2ban-client set openclaw-ssh unbanip <IP>\"\n","path":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/healthcheck/scripts/integrations/fail2ban-integrate.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":87433,"output":1458,"cacheRead":891,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89782,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776851440998,"responseId":"0637ccf14cbf3c872148c757934aa33b"}}
