{"type":"message","id":"dddbe4cf","parentId":"04613b9d","timestamp":"2026-04-22T09:56:30.569Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gjrhgmznat2a_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"</body>\n</html>\nEOF\n            ;;\n    esac\n}\n\n# Run security audit and capture results\nrun_audit() {\n    local output_format=$1\n    local report_file=\"$REPORT_DIR/security-audit-$output_format.$output_format\"\n    \n    log \"Generating $output_format report: $report_file\"\n    \n    case $output_format in\n        json)\n            # Generate JSON report\n            generate_header json > \"$report_file\"\n            \n            # Add system info\n            cat >> \"$report_file\" << 'JSONEOF'\n  \"system\": {\n    \"openclaw_version\": \"unknown\",\n    \"update_available\": false,\n    \"firewall_status\": \"unknown\"\n  },\n  \"findings\": [\nJSONEOF\n            \n            # Capture audit results\n\n[120 more lines in file. Use offset=130 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776851790568}}
{"type":"message","id":"c2cf6920","parentId":"dddbe4cf","timestamp":"2026-04-22T09:56:39.316Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到问题了 - 脚本中有一个 log 函数，但在某些情况下它可能被系统命令覆盖。让我修复这个问题，使用更安全的函数名。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9nv2l4l8fw6s_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/test-report.sh << 'EOF'\n#!/bin/bash\nset -e\n\nREPORT_DIR=\"/tmp/openclaw-reports\"\nmkdir -p \"$REPORT_DIR\"\n\nBLUE='\\033[0;34m'\nGREEN='\\033[0;32m'\nNC='\\033[0m'\n\necho -e \"${BLUE}=== Testing Report Generator ===${NC}\"\n\n# Simple test\necho \"Test 1: Creating JSON report...\"\ncat > \"$REPORT_DIR/test.json\" << 'JSONEOF'\n{\n  \"report\": \"test\",\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"$(date)\"\n}\nJSONEOF\n\necho \"Test 2: Creating Markdown report...\"\ncat > \"$REPORT_DIR/test.md\" << 'MDEOF'\n# Test Report\n\nGenerated at: $(date)\nMDEOF\n\necho \"Test 3: Creating HTML report...\"\ncat > \"$REPORT_DIR/test.html\" << 'HTMLEOF'\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head><title>Test</title></head>\n<body><h1>Test Report</h1></body>\n</html>\nHTMLEOF\n\necho -e \"${GREEN}✅ All test reports created!${NC}\"\nls -lh \"$REPORT_DIR\"\nEOF\n\nchmod +x /tmp/test-report.sh && bash /tmp/test-report.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":540,"output":360,"cacheRead":101243,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102143,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776851790571,"responseId":"0637ce4f0f2d171cc823dd93df7b9e61"}}
